column2: SELECT TOP #  s.plate,s.mjd,s.fiberid,s.z,s.zErr,s.zWarning,s.class,p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj  FROM ..SpecObj as s  JOIN ..Galaxy AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  JOIN Galaxy AS p ON s.bestobjid=p.objid  WHERE s.z > # AND s.zWarning = # AND (s.class = &&&) AND s.z < # AND (p.flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) > #)
